{
  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "id": "寻狗_枯井往下看",
  "entry": "root",
  "meta": {
    "title": "寻狗Demo·枯井狗脸（越界者的下场）"
  },
  "nodes": {
    "root": {
      "type": "switch",
      "cases": [
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "narrative": "scenario_枯井",
              "state": "fled",
              "reached": true
            }
          ],
          "next": "done_1"
        }
      ],
      "defaultNext": "n1"
    },
    "done_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "井边静悄悄的。不看了。",
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "n1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "他把绳子在井栏上绕了两圈，扒着井沿，往下看。",
      "next": "n2"
    },
    "n2": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_枯井往下看",
            "signal": "kujing_looked"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n3"
    },
    "n3": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "叫声，骤停。",
      "next": "n4"
    },
    "n4": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "showOverlayImage",
          "params": {
            "id": "well_nonhuman_face",
            "image": "well_nonhuman_face",
            "xPercent": 50,
            "yPercent": 50,
            "widthPercent": 68
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "playSfx",
          "params": {
            "id": "sfx_heartbeat_bed"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n5"
    },
    "n5": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "井底半截处，蜷着个毛茸茸的东西。仰着脸。冲他。",
      "next": "n6"
    },
    "n6": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "那不是狗的脸。也不是人脸。说不出是什么。",
      "next": "n7"
    },
    "n7": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "waitMs",
          "params": {
            "durationMs": 1300
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n8"
    },
    "n8": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "对看一息。浑身的血，一寸一寸凉下去。",
      "next": "n9"
    },
    "n9": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "hideOverlayImage",
          "params": {
            "id": "well_nonhuman_face"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_枯井往下看",
            "signal": "kujing_stared"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n10"
    },
    "n10": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "像那东西本就在等一个人。看了他一眼——自己没了兴致，慢慢把脸转了回去。",
      "next": "n11"
    },
    "n11": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "关二狗扔下绳子撒腿就跑，一口气跑出半里地才敢回头——井边静悄悄。叫了两天两夜的哭声，没了。",
      "next": "n12"
    },
    "n12": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "（河滩。井底。……这些东西，到底拿俺当什么？）",
      "next": "n_flag"
    },
    "n_flag": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_枯井往下看",
            "signal": "kujing_fled"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "switchScene",
          "params": {
            "targetScene": "雾津街头",
            "targetSpawnPoint": "from_event"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "end1": {
      "type": "end"
    }
  }
}